                                                <strong class="faqs-strong">How do I pay?</strong>
                                   				<p class="faqs-p">You can pay online using debit/credit card or cash at the Just Trip Hub during your bike pickup.</p>
                                   				<strong class="faqs-strong">Is the fuel included in the tariff?</strong>
                                   				<p class="faqs-p">No. Fuel is not included in the rental.  We provide minimal 
                                   				amount of fuel to get the bike to the nearest fuel station. In case there is 
                                   				excess fuel in the bike at the time of return. Just trip is not liable for any 
                                   				refunds for the same.</p>
