                                                <h4 class="faqtitles text-center">Cancellation and refunds</h4>
                                   				<strong class="faqs-strong">Can I Cancel the booking?</strong>
                                   				<p class="faqs-p">Yes. <strong>If you cancel the booking the refund would be made as per the following schedule-</strong></p>
                                   				<ul style="list-style-type: none;">
                                   					<li class="faqs-list" style="color: #F34F4F;">1.Less than 24 hours-No refund</li>
                                   					<li class="faqs-list" style="color: #F34F4F;">2.More than 24 hours-90% refund.</li>
                                   					<li class="faqs-list" style="color: #F34F4F;">3.If we cancel the booking due to break down, non-availability of the bike or any other reason than we provide 100% refund of the rentals received.</li>
                                   				</ul>
                                   				<strong class="faqs-strong">I cancelled my booking. In how many days will I get my refund back?</strong>
                                   				<p class="faqs-p">If you have paid via debit/credit card, you should receive the refund 
                                   				within 3 to 11 working days. However, in the case you don't receive the refund within 
                                   				the mentioned period, write to us @ <a href="mailto:refund@justtrip.in">refund@justtrip.in</a> so we can verify and process 
                                   				the refund at the earliest.</p>
                                            </div>
