                                   				<p class="faqs-p">Yes, the ride has to be at least 18 years.</p>
                                   				<strong class="faqs-strong">Is there any limit on the No'of Kilometers/day?</strong>
                                   				<p class="faqs-p">Yes. Less than 12 Hrs Booking 150 Kms. Between 12 To 24 Hrs 300Kms.</p>
                                   					<ul style="list-style-type: none;">
