                                   				<strong class="faqs-strong">What If the Bike gets Broke Down? What should I do?</strong>
                                   				<p class="faqs-p">Call us @ +91-9663133008 and we'll help you out. Customer care services 
                                   				are open 7am to 12pm, 365 days a week.</p>
                                   				<strong class="faqs-strong">What If I return the bike late because the bike broke down? Will I be fined?</strong>
                                   				<p class="faqs-p">If case of broke down you should call us and report @ +91-9663133008. If the reason 
                                   				is deemed genuine and we verify if from our GPS feedback. You will not be charged any 
                                   				penalties.</p>
                                   				<strong class="faqs-strong">What happens if the bike has been damaged?</strong>
                                   				<p class="faqs-p">Oopz.. The repair estimate will be provided by our service manager. 
                                   				If the estimate is below Rs:10000 the customer has to bear the entire amount while returning 
                                   				the vehicle. However, in case the estimated amount surpasses Rs:10000 limit insurance will 
                                   				be claimed against the vehicle. The customer is liable to pay the estimated amount upfront. 
                                   				Once the insurance amount is received by the company, Just trip will add daily rental to its 
                                   				downtime and refund back the differential amount. Please read our insurance policy for more 
                                   				information.</p>
